      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Tad fuhtija tee Wihri no\nGibeona pee Josuü̈s Lehgeri us\nGilgalu/fazzidami: Ne atranji\ntavu Rohku no taveem Kalpeem:\nNahz tikkuſchi / un tsglahbi\nmuhs/ un palihds mums/ jo wiſ-\nſti Kehniini to Amoriteeu/ kas Kal-\nnds dshwo/ irr prett mums fa-\npulzeifschees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Tad zehlahs Josuü̈s us aug-\nschu no Gilgala/ winsch un wiſſi\nKarra-Wihri ar winnu / un wiſ-\nſi / kam Stiprums un Spehks\nbija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un tas KUNGS fazzija us\nJosuit: Ne bibstees preekſch win-\nneem/ jo es efimu tohs tavā Roh-\nkā nodewis / Ne weenam buhs\ntava Preekſcha pastahweht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Ta nahze Josuü̈s prepeschi\npahr winneem/zaur wiſfu Nakti\nus augſchu eedams no Gilgata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Un tas KUNGS isbee-\ndeja tohs Israēta Preekſcha/ un\nwinsch kawe tohs ar leelu Rauscha-\nnu Gibeonā / un dsinnahs teem\npakkat us to Zettu / kas us Bet-\nObronu tekk / un kawe tohs lihds\nAsekai un Makedai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un kad tee preekſch Isra-\neus to Zettu / kas us\nna Bet-Ohrona/ tad\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "nomette tas KUNGS lee\nKrusta- Gabbalus us teim\nDebbes/ lihds Asekai/ ka tee n\nmirre/ tur bija wairak/ kas\nKruffas nomtre/ ne ka tee Isr\neka Behrti ar Sohbinu nokau\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Tad runnaja Josuü̈s\nto KUNGU tai Deena/ kad t\nKUNGS tohs Amoriteeus n\ndewe Israēta Preekſcha/ un fo\nzija preekſch Israēlu : Sau\nstahwi kluffu eekſch Gibeona/\ntu Mehnes Ahjalona Eeletiā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Tad stahweja ta Sau\nkluffu/ un tas Mehnes pasta-\nweja / teekams tee Laudis pre-\nfaweem Eenaidnekeem bija o\nreebuschees: Neggi tas rakstihs\nirr eekſch to Taifno Grahmata\nTa stahweja ta Saule Debbs\nWiddi kluffu/un ne steidsahs n\neet weenu zauru Deenn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Un ne weena Deena\nbija lihds ka ta Deena / ne\npreekſch winnas/ nedā pehz wi-\nnas/ kad tas KUNGS wee\nWihra Balksnei paklausija /\ntas KUNGS karroja preek-\nIsraēlu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Tad atgreeſahs Josuü̈\nun wiſſe Israēls ar winnu Le-\ngeri us Gilgalu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Bet schee peezi Kehni-\nbija behguſchi/ un apflehpusche-\neekſch tahs Allas pee Makeda-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un Josuüm tappe paflu-\ndinahts un fazzihfs: Tee pee-\nKehniati irr atrasti / apflehpu-\nschees tai Allā pee Makedas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Tad fazzija Josuü̈s: W\n"
    }
  ],
